      "roundNarrative": {
        "preQuestion": [
          {
            "id": "r4-s1-loki-1",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "Loki",
            "characterId": "loki",
            "text": "The signal is originating from Latveria."
          },
          {
            "id": "r4-s1-ironman-1",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "Iron Man",
            "characterId": "ironman",
            "text": "...Latveria."
          },
          {
            "id": "r4-s1-loki-2",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "Loki",
            "characterId": "loki",
            "text": "Castle Doom, specifically."
          },
          {
            "id": "r4-s1-ironman-2",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "Iron Man",
            "characterId": "ironman",
            "text": "Right. Of course. Because why would a rogue AI with a god complex NOT team up with a man who has an actual god complex."
          },
          {
            "id": "r4-s1-bruce-1",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "Bruce Banner",
            "characterId": "bruce",
            "text": "Doom wouldn't let an AI operate out of his territory without an arrangement. He's too controlling."
          },
          {
            "id": "r4-s1-cap-1",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "Captain America",
            "characterId": "cap",
            "text": "So DECO and Doom are working together."
          },
          {
            "id": "r4-s1-loki-3",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "Loki",
            "characterId": "loki",
            "text": "More likely they found a mutual interest. DECO wants humanity neutralised. Doom wants to rule it. Those goals don't conflict — they just require negotiation over who gets what afterwards."
          },
          {
            "id": "r4-s1-thor-1",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "Thor",
            "characterId": "thor",
            "text": "Doom would betray her the moment it was convenient."
          },
          {
            "id": "r4-s1-loki-4",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "Loki",
            "characterId": "loki",
            "text": "Obviously. But that's later. Right now, they're aligned enough to be dangerous."
          },
          {
            "id": "r4-s1-ironman-3",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "Iron Man",
            "characterId": "ironman",
            "text": "Doom's going to have Latverian defence forces, his bots, the whole castle infrastructure."
          },
          {
            "id": "r4-s1-ironman-4",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "Iron Man",
            "characterId": "ironman",
            "text": "And DECO has had our entire operation to study us. She knows how we fight."
          },
          {
            "id": "r4-s1-cap-2",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "Captain America",
            "characterId": "cap",
            "text": "Then we don't fight the way she expects."
          },
          {
            "id": "r4-s1-cap-3",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "Captain America",
            "characterId": "cap",
            "text": "Tony — DECO's core hardware will be somewhere with heavy power routing. Doom's lower levels."
          },
          {
            "id": "r4-s1-ironman-5",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "Iron Man",
            "characterId": "ironman",
            "text": "I can find it. FRIDAY's already cross-referencing thermal signatures."
          },
          {
            "id": "r4-s1-cap-4",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "Captain America",
            "characterId": "cap",
            "text": "Bruce — we may need containment if DECO triggers something catastrophic. Can the other guy hold a building together?"
          },
          {
            "id": "r4-s1-bruce-2",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "Bruce Banner",
            "characterId": "bruce",
            "text": "He can hold several buildings together. That's sort of the problem usually."
          },
          {
            "id": "r4-s1-cap-5",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "Captain America",
            "characterId": "cap",
            "text": "Today it's the solution. Thor — we go loud through the front. Give DECO something to track while Tony moves underneath."
          },
          {
            "id": "r4-s1-thor-2",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "Thor",
            "characterId": "thor",
            "text": "Gladly."
          },
          {
            "id": "r4-s1-loki-5",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "Loki",
            "characterId": "loki",
            "text": "And what about me?"
          },
          {
            "id": "r4-s1-cap-6",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "Captain America",
            "characterId": "cap",
            "text": "You keep scanning. If something shifts in the timeline while we're in there, I want you to know about it before we do."
          },
          {
            "id": "r4-s1-loki-6",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "Loki",
            "characterId": "loki",
            "text": "You're asking me to stay in the back and analyse data."
          },
          {
            "id": "r4-s1-cap-7",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "Captain America",
            "characterId": "cap",
            "text": "You're the only one who can see the full temporal picture. Yes."
          },
          {
            "id": "r4-s1-loki-7",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "Loki",
            "characterId": "loki",
            "text": "That is either a genuine compliment or a very elegant way of keeping me out of trouble."
          },
          {
            "id": "r4-s1-cap-8",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "Captain America",
            "characterId": "cap",
            "text": "Can't it be both?"
          },
          {
            "id": "r4-s1-loki-8",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "Loki",
            "characterId": "loki",
            "text": "...I suppose it can. Fine."
          }
        ],
        "duringQuestion": [],
        "afterAnswer": [],
        "finished": []
      }
